{"tid":1139764,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"見到楊潮凱就會諗起佢老婆曾經係高登寫既故","createTime":"2019-05-05T13:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T14:12:26.000Z","uid":94876,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d4485a99ec2ea2c23de856a76a9ac8d79d6b279a","tid":1139764,"uid":94876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T13:19:40.000Z","msg":"見到佢上流行金曲五十年 就諗起以前係高登睇到佢老婆寫既故<br />\n當年應該仲係播天與地無耐 楊潮凱仲係連電視見過佢都唔太記得既角色<br />\n個時佢老婆比左好少貼士 啲人上tvb個網頁到逐個揾<br />\n開左估之後幾年有留意多左呢個演員 佢都真係好似老婆寫咁對感情認真 幾乎零緋聞<br />\n<br />\n岩岩無聊google 原本佢地仔都生埋了<br />\n當年追故好似婚都未結<br />\n有無人當年都有追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"420e95a12abbb7397b75380e577bdfdaaf90525c","tid":1139764,"uid":211461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T13:21:46.000Z","msg":"好少睇故 有無link?"},{"pid":"c0593b1414cea1369bbba84cd2c3734d67615950","tid":1139764,"uid":148438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T13:26:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"651b9d1ee668b82bbefb9a0c36cf647730f15c33","tid":1139764,"uid":105715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T13:28:52.000Z","msg":"咪戇鳩，樂易玲自己寫架"},{"pid":"2936193e839315d025ad3fb4f2fe15080e387cf6","tid":1139764,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T13:57:14.000Z","msg":"佢而家真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2345579/org/6023147fbe110a0ea76190afe989de10.jpg/s6yGfuM10oCdKEbVQLqDfXy1GnfO4aB1hHC1KYRwtSk?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2345579%2Forg%2F6023147fbe110a0ea76190afe989de10.jpg%2Fs6yGfuM10